=== Numidya ɣ uzmz n Masinissa ===
Iga [[masinissa]] yan zɣ igldan lli bahra ittawsn itgldit numidya , ilul ɣ [[Sirta]] li ityawssan s [[kestentina]] ɣin aɣ isker lɛasima itgldit ns men ras li riga agllid ,ila ukan soul usmDl n ugellid ad ɣ tmazirt an , ikkatin masinissa ityawssan s tuggas nns bahra ichdan rtiminiɣ d limurat nns , ɣikan af iga tmi iwmzizzil nes li dis ikcmn romnidan zund [[Sifaks]] ula [[Hanibal]] ɣ umzizzil niɣd imaɣen n ZAMA 202 (izwarn talalit n [[Ɛisa]] , tamatart li bahra itussan f masinissa achnyal li siberh atigan d (Akal n Tfriqt iydebab nns) teder tageldit n numidya ɣ wussan kigan dzher rkolo tazɣiwin n tudert mach taliɣen ifel masinissa lhsab tgat is itto ayserso limurat nmara ikoso lkursi n tgeldit nns iɣ iggez Akal ,achko ɣikan af jran kigan d imaɣen ngr tarwa nns ayliɣ imut , kchmnd irumiyn (Rouman) sluzzun tagldit ftarwa nns skrad fkan i [[Masipsa]] saha ig agelid numidya yamz gmas [[Rilassa]] limurat nimaɣn ig anmɣur n limorat ntminiɣ yamz gmatsen wiss 3 [[Mastanbal]] anmɣur yattuyn ntgldit macc izdar [[Masipsa]] ad mara ikoso madsalan aylir mouten aytmas ryan ouzemz ur bahra yaggugn  mach rikli yad ijran ibabas Masinissa arays ijro ula nettan ayliɣ immut nkern imaɣn nger tarwa nns [[Adherbal]] , [[Himepsil]] ɣikan af dar af toufa Roma matra tkid dar afus atfoko imchibukn ngratsen , walakin iga [[Yugrtn]] tachajiɛt rlant tirrukza dwatig irewas dadas [[Masinissa]] urasen ikebil ɣunckan

=== Numidya ɣ uzmz n Yugrtn ===
Igan [[Yugrtn]] Tuggas nss, izdar ad ismun tagldit issinf aytmas ɣuɣaras isker ɣ [[Sirta]] lɛasima nns ɣikli isker dadas , izdar aynru Roma ɣ kigan n imaɣen isyagasen kigan dlɛsker inɣ kigan gisen mac tuckad tagara nns ɣikli issutr umzruy nirumiyn f ufus nyan unmɣur n mouritan Tamaziɣt atigan d [[Buxus]] li sers iɣdern ayliɣas imdi netan d Roma , ityamaz ikchem abniq (lhebs) aylliɣ tid tlkem lmut ( at iwala rebi stmella)

Ayliɣ imut Yugrtn tslouza dar Roma tageldit f krad igzman yan yumzt umddakl nesen [[Buxus]] d yan i GHOUDA d ɣaylid iɣaman isaha i MASTA -NONZOUS

=== Numidya ɣ uzmz n [[Yuba I]] ===
[[Afaylu:Juba denarius in support of Pompey against Cesar 60 46 BCE.jpg |right|thumb|250 px|Yuba I]]
Yugad Yuba disiga yan ugllid amaynu n tagldit Numidya ig ayyaw n [[Yugrtn]] iga wasarens yuba amzwaru , ikkatin ugllid ad ar isstur ad ismun tagldit kullut afad ad iskr yat tgldit ibiddn fidarn nns infassayn ɣ ufus n Roma ɣikli yadlli ran lajdud nns [[Yugrtn]] d Masinissa , ɣ uzɣgas n [[48]] ( izwarn talalit n [[Σisa]]) ggrand kra nimaɣn ngr [[Pomyus]] d [[Sizar]] f manwa gitsn rayg agllid n roma ɣikan af yiws nettan i [[Pomyus]] mac ca vimavn tgrad iwmzizzil nns sizar , lid yawsn vumnid nns i [[Buxus]] wissin (buvud) wissin afad ad nrun [[Yuba I|Yuba amzwaru]] , li irwln gr ifassn nnsn mac igan tigiri iwssan nns inɣ agayyuns ryan umzizzil ngras d yan unmɣur n roma 
s lmut n [[Yuba I]] nfda tagldit numidya tmun ussan nns ɣ uzɣgas n 46 (iz-ta n [[Σisa|Σsa]])

